title: Family Guy Presents: Stewie Kills Lois and Lois Kills Stewie
genres: Animation, Comedy, Action, Adventure, Crime, Thriller, Music, TV Movie
overview: "Stewie Kills Lois" and "Lois Kills Stewie" is a two-part episode of the sixth season of the animated comedy series Family Guy, which was originally produced for the end of Season 5.
